{"tid":910490,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"男人矮真係慘過窮+樣衰+一事無成加埋","createTime":"2018-11-21T08:27:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T09:29:19.000Z","uid":58316,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"467f2fd8d7d3b2320903985472fc395fe3d3382f","tid":910490,"uid":58316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:27:41.000Z","msg":"由2019年1月1日起<br />\n男人標準身高<br />\n將會調整至五呎十<br />\n凡矮過五呎十<br />\n而又係1990年1月1日後<br />\n出生既成年男性<br />\n無論職場上<br />\n家庭崗位上<br />\n將會受到更嚴格限制<br />\n講真<br />\n90後<br />\n冇五呎十真係矮<br />\n冇五呎九真係好矮<br />\n窮咪打多份工<br />\n一係綜援<br />\n樣衰咪脫毒<br />\n再樣衰d咪整容<br />\n一事無成咪揾野學<br />\n通街學店你有心就得<br />\n矮真係天下間幾多男人<br />\n不能磨滅既痛<br />\n永遠擺係心底既遺憾<br />\n錢帶唔走<br />\n事業到頭來一場空<br />\n靚老婆終有一日講再見<br />\n但唯獨係矮<br />\n將會隨你五呎身軀而去<br />\n你<br />\n就係矮既化身<br />\n你既人生<br />\n同矮劃上等號<br />\n你=矮<br />\n終身俾呢座五呎監獄困住<br />\n直到終有一日<br />\n化煙<br />\n解脫"},{"pid":"613835a502a448bbb065738dfb290e395d5bd374","tid":910490,"uid":20066,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:28:49.000Z","msg":"又矮又窮又樣衰又一事無成"},{"pid":"bc63232ea506d9ea3e64ddfa542dc68a9410bc50","tid":910490,"uid":219056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:29:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0390bd75f5341cf8da9541bba332ee89033c431b","tid":910490,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:31:39.000Z","msg":"你五呎十?"},{"pid":"a287c40d72550538357f435c3fc543298772d460","tid":910490,"uid":129660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:32:46.000Z","msg":"收皮啦"},{"pid":"d1d30dc81d3b634ea02aac11d16c315e6679b64a","tid":910490,"uid":161190,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:39:41.000Z","msg":"on9 男人一事無錢係慘過矮+樣衰<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/efSdQuw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FefSdQuw.png&h=6fd4c622&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76b01bef4